thread.title: Terri Lines
thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Terri Lines

author: Terri Lines
title: Terri Lines
text: Very very impressed, and happy to recommend to anyone. At $200 per month for 2 boxes (which held an entire 3 brm household's worth of stuff) was far more economical than any other storage facility and in my case (being a single female) having the boxes delivered and picked up was an absoluted godsend.
